2007: "The Case for Energy-Proportional Computing"
__________________________________________________

- focus on energy and utilization relative to memory and disk subsystems
- reference to the complex nature of the network external to the system
- emphasis on mode of operation of servers vs laptops (i.e. general purpose devices)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2014: "Towards Energy-Proportionality for Large-Scale Latency-Critical Workloads"
_________________________________________________________________________________

- presents Pegasus: a feedback controller that adjusts power settings
- emphasis on shortcomings of processor frequency scaling subsystems
- exposes headroom in latency measurements that calls for a tradeoff between latency and power

